metadata_description: Fast SNMP scanner. onesixtyone takes a different approach to SNMP scanning. It takes advantage of the fact that SNMP is a connectionless protocol and sends all SNMP requests as fast as it can. Then the scanner waits for responses to come back and logs them in a fashion similar to Nmap ping sweeps
